data.description: Absolutely stunning custom-built 2011 home! Heated 1946 sq ft, on the first floor and 256 sq.ft. 2nd floor Bonus, plus an attached 2 car garage. Numerous upgrades and maintained well by the owners.  Venture inside to be greeted by a spacious semi open-concept design where the kitchen takes center stage, boasting beautiful countertops, walk-in pantry, and a comprehensive suite of stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, stove, microwave, and dishwasher.  This stunning split floor plan home presents 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 pristine bathrooms, and a welcoming private rear yard, perfect for those cherished moments of relaxation and entertainment. Make this Dream Home your Forever Home by calling to view it today!
